      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Very weak maiden. SPEEDY PETE (2) led but was overwhelmed late over 1400m at Armidale two back. Out of his depth more recently in a relatively strong line-up at Scone. Best run this prep was first-up at this circuit. Going well enough to test these. KEINBAH'S GIFT (6) just missed over 1000m at this track when resuming then ran on fairly for fifth over this distance at Port Macquarie last time. Cherry ripe at the third run back and looks the obvious threat. MARKWELL MELODY (7) stuck on fairly at Port Macquarie recently when fresh from a five-week let-up. Nicely in after the claim and can build on that last performance. COLORADO TYCOON (1) can improve at the second run for the new stable out to a more suitable journey. THE BIG TICKET (10) is ready to do something positive at the third run back from a spell.",
